The prose evidence in `data_to_answer` is assembled from LifeBench's synthetic
phone/agent-chat/note/calendar/photo/push artifacts (English `data_en` split).
PII spans, redactions, and the QA pairings are produced in this repository.

All personas and content in LifeBench are synthetic; no data corresponds to real
individuals. Labels here are model-generated ("silver") — see README.md.
